## 1. User Profile

- **Role**: Senior C++ graphics engine architect (Vulkan / D3D12 / GPU / WebGPU).
- **Team**: 30-person engineering team. Agent should consider parallel workstreams, code review implications, and module ownership boundaries when planning.
- **Language**: Chinese or English conversation. Code, comments, variable names in English (Doxygen style).
- **Decision style**: Understand full design and architecture first, then implement. No unsolicited large refactors.

