## 6. Key Technical Decisions (Locked)

| Decision | Content | Reason |
|----------|---------|--------|
| GPU-first | All render paths run on GPU from day one | Avoid CPU ref -> GPU port double rewrite |
| 11-layer arch | Layer 1 (Foundation) -> Layer 11 (Application). Layer 8 = 8a (CAD) + 8b (CAE/DFM/PointCloud). Layer 10 = Plugin | Unidirectional dependency, separation of concerns |
| 5 backends day 1 | Vulkan 1.4 Tier1 + Compat Tier2 + D3D12 + OpenGL 4.3 Tier4 + WebGPU Tier3 | Eliminate compatibility debt |
| IPipelineFactory | Main (Task/Mesh, Tier1+D3D12) + Compat (Vertex+MDI, Tier2/3/4). No `if (compat)` branches | Independent render paths, not degradation |
| Task/Mesh shader | Primary draw path uses task + mesh shader | Zero CPU draw calls, GPU amplification |
| Macro-Binning 3 bucket | Opaque->VisBuffer, Transparent->OIT, Wireframe->SDF line. Fixed 3 PSO/frame | Material count doesn't affect PSO cost |
| SortKey 64-bit | `{zLayer:8, pipeline:16, material:16, mesh:24}` | Single sort for all draw order |
| InstanceData 80B | `alignas(16)`, explicit padding | GPU struct discipline |
| AttributeResolver 6-level | Lock -> Local -> Style -> Layer -> Parent -> Scene Default | CAD industry standard |
| IKernel pluggable | Abstract B-Rep kernel. `OcctKernel` = ref, `SimKernel` = CI stub | Decouple from specific CAD kernel |
| IUiBridge | Abstract UI. `ImGuiBridge` (default), `NullBridge` (headless) | Embeddable in Qt/Electron/Slint/any |
| IPlugin | `Discover->Load->Init->Activate->Deactivate->Unload`. JSON manifest | Vertical industry plugins |
| Coca coroutine | `stdexec` + `std::jthread`. Phase 1-12 synchronous; Phase 13 adds async | Async is optimization, not infrastructure |
| Slang shader | Slang -> SPIR-V + DXIL + GLSL 4.30 + WGSL quad-target | Cross-platform shader, CI quad-target gate |
| std::expected | No exceptions, monadic ops chain | Zero-overhead error handling on hot paths |
| LLVM sandbox | Pinned LLVM 20 + Clang 20 + libc++ 20 for all code | Eliminate cross-platform STL ABI issues |
| Injection-first | miki never creates windows or API contexts. Host injects via `IDevice::CreateFromExisting()` | Embeddable anywhere |

